{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1679-10a_117", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Placet de l’Amour]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", octobre 1679 (première partie) [tome 10], p. 117-122."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il court une Galanterie fort agreable dont je me croy obligé de vous faire part. Elle est d’une Dame de qualité. La maniere fine & délicate dont cette Piece est tournée, fait connoistre la beauté de son esprit. On juge aisément qu’elle a esté faite sur quelque Arrest obtenu contre les projets de deux Amans. La Réponse que vous trouverez en suite est un Inpromptu, fait par une Personne tres-spirituelle, qui fait parler l’Ombre d’une Illustre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Placet"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "de l’amour, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[3]", "text": "au roy."}], "attributes": {"type": "head"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Grand Roy, qui redonnez le repos à la Terre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ah ne permettez pas qu’on me fasse la guerre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand vous avez marché, mes Sujets à l’envy"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Par tout aux grands Exploits vous ont-ils pas suivy ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Si j’ay sçeu dans les cœurs inspirer la tendresse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "La Gloire en a toûjours demeuré la maîtresse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Et l’on a veu souvent par vos braves Guerriers"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Myrthes négligez pour les sanglans Lauriers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais les jours sont venus où l’Europe respire ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Alliée, ou soûmise à vostre heureux Empire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "J’entens de toutes parts que l’on chante la Paix,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Et je croyois me voir au but de mes souhaits."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Je croyois qu'on pourroit dans ce temps favorable"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Retrouver le plaisir d’aimer & d’estre aimable ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Cependant quand je fais ces innocens projets,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "J’apprens que contre moy l’on donne des Arrests."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Iris se laisse voir, elle est charmante & belle,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est d’illustres cœurs qui s’enflâment pour elle,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur cela l’on se plaint & l’on porte l’excés"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Jusqu’à luy vouloir faire un criminel Procés."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "On n’ose plus aimer, qu’aussitost l’on n’informe ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Juges assemblez, par leurs Decrets en forme,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Prétendent aujourd’huy détruire mon pouvoir,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[24]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[24]/text()[1]", "text": "Et punir les Amans quand ils font leur devoir."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[25]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[25]/text()[1]", "text": "J’appelle à Vous, Grand Roy, d’une telle injustice,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[26]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[26]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne laissez pas régner ce dangereux caprice,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[27]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[27]/text()[1]", "text": "Ordonnez à vos grands & sages Parlemens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[28]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[28]/text()[1]", "text": "De vuider les Procés, sans en faire aux Amans."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[29]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[29]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous avez, en mettant Victoire sur Victoire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[30]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[30]/text()[1]", "text": "Elevé vostre Trône au faiste de la Gloire."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[31]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[31]/text()[1]", "text": "De là, quand il vous plaist rappeller les Plaisirs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[32]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[32]/text()[1]", "text": "Suis-je pas toûjours prest à remplir vos desirs ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[33]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[33]/text()[1]", "text": "Prenez donc mon party contre la Tyrannie"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[34]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[34]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui s’attache à troubler les douceurs de la vie."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[35]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[35]/text()[1]", "text": "On me verroit bientost quitter ce beau sejour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[36]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[36]/text()[1]", "text": "S’il falloit pour aimer, un Arrest de la Cour."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[37]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[37]/text()[1]", "text": "Daignez par un seul mot dissiper tant de brigues"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[38]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[38]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui pensent avoir droit sur mes tendres intrigues,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[39]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[39]/text()[1]", "text": "Et déclarez enfin, pour finir leurs erreurs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]/text()[1]", "text": "Que "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "louis"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]/text()[2]", "text": " & l’Amour sont seuls maistres des cœurs."}]}]}]}